animations that do not exist. We do not have the resources to create them.\\n</important>\\n\\n<user-request>\\n  Create a website about space exploration\\n</user-request>\\n\\n<task>\\n  REMINDER: \\n          Generate the detailed plan for the section based on the provided information.\\n          Follow the specific instructions provided for the given section type.\\n</task>\\n\\n<structured-output>\\n  You must format your output as a JSON value that adheres to a given \\\"JSON Schema\\\" instance.\\n\\n\\\"JSON Schema\\\" is a declarative language that allows you to annotate and validate JSON documents.\\n\\nFor example, the example \\\"JSON Schema\\\" instance {{\\\"properties\\\": {{\\\"foo\\\": {{\\\"description\\\": \\\"a list of test words\\\", \\\"type\\\": \\\"array\\\", \\\"items\\\": {{\\\"type\\\": \\\"string\\\"}}}}}}, \\\"required\\\": [\\\"foo\\\"]}}\\nwould match an object with one required property, \\\"foo\\\". The \\\"type\\\" property specifies \\\"foo\\\" must be an \\\"array\\\", and the \\\"description\\\" property semantically describes it as \\\"a list of test words\\\". The items within \\\"foo\\\" must be strings.\\nThus, the object {{\\\"foo\\\": [\\\"bar\\\", \\\"baz\\\"]}} is a well-formatted instance of this example \\\"JSON Schema\\\". The object {{\\\"properties\\\": {{\\\"foo\\\": [\\\"bar\\\", \\\"baz\\\"]}}}} is not well-formatted.\\n\\nYour output will be parsed and type-checked according to the provided schema instance, so make sure all fields in your output match the schema exactly and there are no trailing commas!\\n\\nHere is the JSON Schema instance your output must adhere to. Include the enclosing markdown codeblock:\\n```json\\n{\\\"type\\\":\\\"object\\\",\\\"properties\\\":{\\\"suggestedComponents\\\":{\\\"anyOf\\\":[{\\\"type\\\":\\\"array\\\",\\\"items\\\":{\\\"type\\\":\\\"string\\\"}},{\\\"type\\\":\\\"null\\\"}],\\\"description\\\":\\\"List of suggested Shadcn UI components for this section.\\\"},\\\"headline\\\":{\\\"type\\\":[\\\"string\\\",\\\"null\\\"],\\\"description\\\":\\\"The headline for the social proof section (e.g., 'Trusted By').\\\"},\\\"contentType\\\":{\\\"type\\\":\\\"string\\\",\\\"enum\\\":[\\\"Logos\\\",\\\"Stats\\\",\\\"Awards\\\",\\\"Mix\\\"],\\\"description\\\":\\\"The primary type of social proof displayed.\\\"},\\\"paragraphs\\\":{\\\"type\\\":[\\\"string\\\",\\\"null\\\"],\\\"description\\\":\\\"Paragraphs of text to be included in the section.\\\"},\\\"logos\\\":{\\\"anyOf\\\":[{\\\"type\\\":\\\"array\\\",\\\"items\\\":{\\\"type\\\":\\\"string\\\"}},{\\\"type\\\":\\\"null\\\"}],\\\"description\\\":\\\"List of company names or identifiers for logos.\\\"},\\\"stats\\\":{\\\"anyOf\\\":[{\\\"type\\\":\\\"array\\\",\\\"items\\\":{\\\"type\\\":\\\"object\\\",\\\"properties\\\":{\\\"value\\\":{\\\"type\\\":\\\"string\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"The statistic value (e.g., '10,000+', '98%').\\\"},\\\"label\\\":{\\\"type\\\":\\\"string\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"The label or context for the statistic (e.g., 'Active Users', 'Customer Satisfaction').\\\"}},\\\"required\\\":[\\\"value\\\",\\\"label\\\"],\\\"additionalProperties\\\":false}},{\\\"type\\\":\\\"null\\\"}],\\\"description\\\":\\\"List of key statistics.\\\"},\\\"awards\\\":{\\\"anyOf\\\":[{\\\"type\\\":\\\"array\\\",\\\"items\\\":{\\\"type\\\":\\\"string\\\"}},{\\\"type\\\":\\\"null\\\"}],\\\"description\\\":\\\"List of award names or badges.\\\"}},\\\"required\\\":[\\\"suggestedComponents\\\",\\\"headline\\\",\\\"contentType\\\",\\\"paragraphs\\\",\\\"logos\\\",\\\"stats\\\",\\\"awards\\\"],\\\"additionalProperties\\\":false,\\\"$schema\\\":\\\"http://json-schema.org/draft-07/schema#\\\"}\\n```\\n</structured-output>\"}"
