column\\n- Stackable navigation links\\n- Centered content on smaller screens\\n\\n5. Recommended Components:\\n- @/components/ui/navigation-menu.tsx\\n- @/components/ui/separator.tsx\\n- @/components/ui/button.tsx (for social media links)\\n\\n6. Additional Elements:\\n- Copyright notice\\n- Privacy policy link\\n- Social media icons (GitHub, Twitter, LinkedIn)\\n- Optional newsletter signup\\n\\nThe footer maintains the inspirational, scientifically credible tone of the space exploration theme while providing clear, functional navigation.\"}]}"
