            "params": [],
            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-3-5-haiku-latest\",\"temperature\":0,\"top_k\":-1,\"top_p\":-1,\"stream\":false,\"max_tokens\":2048,\"tools\":[{\"name\":\"extract\",\"description\":\"A function available to call.\",\"input_schema\":{\"type\":\"object\",\"properties\":{\"availableSections\":{\"type\":\"array\",\"items\":{\"type\":\"string\"},\"description\":\"List of available sections for the Nav.\"},\"componentType\":{\"type\":\"string\",\"const\":\"Nav\"}},\"required\":[\"availableSections\",\"componentType\"],\"additionalProperties\":false,\"$schema\":\"http://json-schema.org/draft-07/schema#\"}}],\"tool_choice\":{\"type\":\"tool\",\"name\":\"extract\"},\"thinking\":{\"type\":\"disabled\"},\"messages\":[{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":\"Help the user plan a section of their website.\"},{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":\"I'll help plan the Navigation (Nav) section for the space exploration website. Based on the provided context and guidelines, here's a comprehensive plan:\\n\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"availableSections\\\": [\\n    \\\"Hero\\\",\\n    \\\"Features\\\", \\n    \\\"Benefits\\\", \\n    \\\"Testimonials\\\", \\n    \\\"SocialProof\\\", \\n    \\\"CTA\\\"\\n  ]\\n}\\n```\\n\\nDetailed Section Plan for Navigation:\\n\\n1. Layout Description:\\n- Horizontal navigation bar spanning full width of the page\\n- Centered logo on the left side\\n- Navigation menu items aligned to the right\\n- Responsive design that collapses to hamburger menu on mobile\\n\\n2. Visual Styling:\\n- Background: Deep space dark blue/black (#0D1117)\\n- Text Color: Bioluminescent blue-white (#E6F1FF)\\n- Typography: Clean, modern sans-serif (e.g., Inter or Roboto)\\n- Hover effects: Subtle glow effect mimicking starlight\\n\\n3. Navigation Menu Items:\\n- Logo: \\\"SpaceVoyage\\\" (clickable, returns to home)\\n- Menu Items:\\n  1. Home (/#hero)\\n  2. Features (/#features)\\n  3. Benefits (/#benefits)\\n  4. Testimonials (/#testimonials)\\n  5. CTA (/#cta)\\n\\n4. Recommended Components:\\n- Use Shadcn UI's `navigation-menu.tsx`\\n- Use Shadcn UI's `button.tsx` for CTA/action buttons\\n- React Router for navigation links\\n\\n5. Responsiveness:\\n- Mobile: Hamburger menu using Shadcn UI's `sheet.tsx`\\n- Collapse menu into sliding side panel\\n- Maintain brand color scheme and styling\\n\\n6. Interaction Notes:\\n- Smooth scroll to section anchors\\n- Active section highlighted with subtle indicator\\n- Hover states with gentle animation\\n\\n7. Accessibility Considerations:\\n- Keyboard navigable\\n- Clear focus states\\n- Proper aria labels\\n- High color contrast\\n\\nThe navigation will embody the brand's inspirational and scientific tone, creating a sense of wonder while providing clear, intuitive website navigation.\"}]}"
