            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-3-5-haiku-latest\",\"temperature\":0,\"top_k\":-1,\"top_p\":-1,\"stream\":false,\"max_tokens\":2048,\"tools\":[{\"name\":\"extract\",\"description\":\"A function available to call.\",\"input_schema\":{\"type\":\"object\",\"properties\":{\"suggestedComponents\":{\"anyOf\":[{\"type\":\"array\",\"items\":{\"type\":\"string\"}},{\"type\":\"null\"}],\"description\":\"List of suggested Shadcn UI components for this section.\"},\"headline\":{\"type\":[\"string\",\"null\"],\"description\":\"The headline for the testimonials section (e.g., 'What Our Customers Say').\"},\"subheadline\":{\"type\":[\"string\",\"null\"],\"description\":\"Optional supporting text below the headline.\"},\"paragraphs\":{\"type\":[\"string\",\"null\"],\"description\":\"Paragraphs of text to be included in the section.\"},\"testimonials\":{\"type\":\"array\",\"items\":{\"type\":\"object\",\"properties\":{\"quote\":{\"type\":\"string\",\"description\":\"The customer's testimonial quote.\"},\"name\":{\"type\":\"string\",\"description\":\"The name of the person providing the testimonial.\"},\"title_company\":{\"type\":\"string\",\"description\":\"Job title and/or company for context.\"},\"location\":{\"type\":[\"string\",\"null\"],\"description\":\"Optional location (e.g., City, State).\"},\"starRating\":{\"type\":[\"number\",\"null\"],\"description\":\"Star rating if applicable (e.g., 4.5 stars).\"}},\"required\":[\"quote\",\"name\",\"title_company\",\"location\",\"starRating\"],\"additionalProperties\":false},\"description\":\"An array of testimonials.\"},\"componentType\":{\"type\":\"string\",\"const\":\"Testimonials\"}},\"required\":[\"suggestedComponents\",\"headline\",\"subheadline\",\"paragraphs\",\"testimonials\",\"componentType\"],\"additionalProperties\":false,\"$schema\":\"http://json-schema.org/draft-07/schema#\"}}],\"tool_choice\":{\"type\":\"tool\",\"name\":\"extract\"},\"thinking\":{\"type\":\"disabled\"},\"messages\":[{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":\"Help the user plan a section of their website.\"},{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":\"I'll help plan the Testimonials section for the space exploration website based on the provided guidelines and requirements. I'll generate a comprehensive section plan that captures the essence of social proof while maintaining the brand's inspirational and scientific tone.\\n\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"suggestedComponents\\\": [\\n    \\\"@/components/ui/card.tsx\\\",\\n    \\\"@/components/ui/avatar.tsx\\\"\\n  ],\\n  \\\"headline\\\": \\\"Voices of Space Pioneers\\\",\\n  \\\"subheadline\\\": \\\"Real Stories from Those Pushing the Boundaries of Human Exploration\\\",\\n  \\\"paragraphs\\\": \\\"Our community represents a diverse group of space enthusiasts, researchers, and dreamers who are actively shaping the future of space exploration. These testimonials showcase the transformative power of joining a movement larger than ourselves.\\\",\\n  \\\"testimonials\\\": [\\n    {\\n      \\\"quote\\\": \\\"I never thought I'd be involved in actual space research. Now I'm contributing to real Mars mission planning!\\\",\\n      \\\"name\\\": \\\"Sarah K.\\\",\\n      \\\"title_company\\\": \\\"Community Research Contributor, SpaceVentures\\\",\\n      \\\"location\\\": \\\"San Francisco, CA\\\",\\n      \\\"starRating\\\": 5.0\\n    },\\n    {\\n      \\\"quote\\\": \\\"The access to cutting-edge space technology and industry experts is unprecedented.\\\",\\n      \\\"name\\\": \\\"Dr. James Chen\\\",\\n      \\\"title_company\\\": \\\"Aerospace Engineer, NASA Collaborative Program\\\",\\n      \\\"location\\\": \\\"Houston, TX\\\", \\n      \\\"starRating\\\": 4.5\\n    }\\n  ]\\n}\\n```\\n\\nLet me break down the key aspects of this section plan:\\n\\n🔍 Section Strategy:\\n- Headline \\\"Voices of Space Pioneers\\\" creates immediate intrigue\\n- Subheadline emphasizes the transformative nature of space exploration\\n- Paragraph provides context and emotional framing for the testimonials\\n\\n💡 Design Considerations:\\n- Use of Card and Avatar components for clean, modern presentation\\n- Leveraging scientific credibility through professional testimonials\\n- Highlighting diverse perspectives (research contributor and aerospace engineer)\\n\\n🎨 Visual Approach:\\n- Align with brand guidelines of deep space imagery\\n- Use constellation-like connecting elements\\n- Incorporate bioluminescent blues and purples\\n- Create a sense of movement and exploration\\n\\n📱 Responsiveness:\\n- Cards will stack vertically on mobile devices\\n- Maintain readability and visual hierarchy across screen sizes\\n\\nThe plan captures the brand's inspirational tone while providing concrete social proof, making space exploration feel accessible and exciting.\\n\\nWould you like me to elaborate on any aspect of the section plan?\"}]}"
          },
